headline.print_headline: Phil Everly, Half of Pioneer Rock Duo, Dies at 74
headline.main: Phil Everly, Half of Pioneer Rock Duo, Dies at 74

lead_paragraph: Phil Everly, one half of the pioneering Everly Brothers harmony duo that sparked the imaginations of rock 'n' roll singers for decades, has died. He was 74.
